Pretty nice story. Basically, big sis is so good at everything she does that lil sis suffers from inferiority complex. She was happy when a senpai appreciated her despite her shortcomings. Turned out that he only fucked her just so he could taste her once. She blamed her sister for how bad her life went, but they managed make up and still be good to each other. Now on present, Big sis got a BF who suffers from a similar situation with lil sis. Big Sis is, as usual, doing pretty well in their company and BF just can't compete with her. That's basically where the story revolves. At first, lil sis hated him. He took advantage of her after all and harasses her constantly. But in the end, she discovered that he's doing this bad stuff to relieve his stress from failing to keep up with big sis. That's where she drew her sympathy for him.
